{"tid":417542,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］Console vs PC","createTime":"2017-09-28T18:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T08:55:10.000Z","uid":97416,"like":13,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d434760ce10c98da367e9f3826582c06917e1168","tid":417542,"uid":97416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T18:10:17.000Z","msg":"其實糾結左好耐 點解咁多人齋玩console唔過當PC<br />\n<br />\n首先console限左你好多野 無得好似pc咁customise 仲要一兩年就換代 仲要逐隻game買而且d game都係一年就再出一次新版 再掠多一獲水<br />\n<br />\n相反pc好多f2p或者比一次錢就無限更新既game 硬件kum玩好多 可以逐d換<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識玩梗係玩console<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> pc萬歲!"},{"pid":"8ebe0f002b59214d01b5107a286c1fff2ce791d3","tid":417542,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T23:14:43.000Z","msg":"pc 麻煩到仆街，又貴"},{"pid":"dc49c08bd097d89a70a64420194bd07a8f6ca72b","tid":417542,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>pc 麻煩到仆街，又貴</blockquote><br />\nconsole上網連線都要課金，game又貴過人，不了"},{"pid":"23d7e633ad02f834a2a3c9eb43f57d0e82bb7948","tid":417542,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T08:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pc 麻煩到仆街，又貴</blockquote><br />\nconsole上網連線都要課金，game又貴過人，不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓? console game買實體版 同steam基本上一樣價喎<br />\n除左steam某時節大特賣先會特別平喎<br />\n<br />\n上網連線要畀錢(有送games) vs 免費(部份games冇自己servers 連線品質較低 同大量外掛<br />\n你自己簡"},{"pid":"529ac89e3f169270e18f3381b8d43e171753857e","tid":417542,"uid":8659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"一兩年就換代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a53a734e9086223038ded18bac4b4a8f1a0eb5","tid":417542,"uid":12285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> steam 玩l4d 2 成日彈game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515716b5a6830d663bdb288eca72a26c2e4dbe91","tid":417542,"uid":130295,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:04:06.000Z","msg":"你砌部機勁過console都唔止console個價錢啦 仲要pc平台穩定性差過console好多"},{"pid":"0920643ef065a5b04db2b2a382e78ba30062b7a1","tid":417542,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你砌部機勁過console都唔止console個價錢啦 仲要pc平台穩定性差過console好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4930cf664fa3c56c00ebdeeb6ab66cdb69ea1b3b","tid":417542,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T11:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你砌部機勁過console都唔止console個價錢啦 仲要pc平台穩定性差過console好多</blockquote><br />\n岩呀，同埋人眼只係望到30fps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a64aeac3f56d4bfa91116e1726b54aad0f93189","tid":417542,"uid":21102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"用手掣玩好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c6ee11efff38d8ff7e1a32a2159321ac4ad886","tid":417542,"uid":49153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"無視價錢<br />\n單計game嘅質素<br />\n一定係PC&gt;all"},{"pid":"eabd4c161c276dcbd1bd8216dabfcb980b0a84ff","tid":417542,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"好多遊戲機大作電腦都冇出過<br />\n你就算等N年後出模擬器<br />\n都模擬唔到好多遊戲機獨家功能或服務<br />\n舉個例<br />\nSwitch單機拆掣就夠雙打<br />\n你電腦玩模擬器就完全體驗唔到個種方便<br />\n<br />\n電腦game因為spec千變萬花<br />\n優化較差、bug較多、online外掛都多<br />\n可以有D display card driver版本令你打機有問題<br />\n用遊戲機打機好少鑊氣<br />\n<br />\nWindows隔一兩年就全球出一次大事<br />\n例如大規模中病毒<br />\n仲成日彈D error message window出黎阻住你打機<br />\n好多人遊戲直播緊都可以彈出Windows強制升級<br />\n<br />\nPC最大優勢可能係玩RTS個類game"},{"pid":"8dec62416ae59cae90f4d9d5249b78117db81cf4","tid":417542,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無視價錢<br />\n單計game嘅質素<br />\n一定係PC&gt;all</blockquote><br />\n鑊氣都多好多<br />\n<br />\n親身買過玩過電腦版遊戲機版NFS同BF3<br />\n遊戲機版少好多問題<br />\nNFS有一代可以冇對多核心CPU優化勁疾<br />\nBF3可以有bug強制彈game單機故事都玩唔到<br />\n要等出patch先無事<br />\n但我玩遊戲機版冇呢D問題<br />\n<br />\n電腦game認真要買D良心game廠出嘅<br />\n先少好多問題"},{"pid":"e17c2c57c05234667db78bd557dc62a5207db453","tid":417542,"uid":20098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"pc 玩單機game 最爽係玩改mod<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa7844a0aa43b51d3081d50758dde72f184aafd","tid":417542,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"仲要一兩年就換代<br />\n你ON9?"},{"pid":"ae7c4b29bd3f2f471ec5c9226ebc46d8561d536f","tid":417542,"uid":138188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:39:01.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d7431fd10f5a4a168d2cc8ed1fe9bdc9212b57","tid":417542,"uid":10422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:47:20.000Z","msg":"睇下班 pc master race <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n彈丸論破v3要出啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/396658/page/17?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/396658/page/17?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2c8c8b970a28152b6a482aceedfa18b08463b813","tid":417542,"uid":61472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:24:21.000Z","msg":"pc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咩game耐玩得過steam<img